We are aware of the sheer size and magnitude of what we are building compared to other 
projects built on the blockchain. A critical element to success will undoubtedly be engaging in 
an in-depth, proof-of-concept and proof-of-technology analysis to ensure the feasibility of the 
undertaking. The end product must be of supreme quality taking into account potential storage 
limitations and network capacity constraints. Our intention is to prove the feasibility and build 
the platform for the greater community to enjoy. 

   



 

